{"tid":222092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MK輝：陳美齡名利場強調自己是UNICEF大使，在NGO界不忘炫富","createTime":"2017-04-29T09:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T03:34:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28fabe5d1c2e4eb3fabe333519c457245f926680","tid":222092,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"關於陳美齡，本來就是日本學術朋友一個很感興趣的研究課題。日本學界的朋友這樣告訴我：陳美齡在學術研討會自稱不懂政治的藝能人，回到演藝人聚會就自居學者；在名利場強調自己的UNICEF大使身份，在NGO界不忘炫富；在真聯合國平台說自己的UNICEF屬於民間，在公民社會則強化「UN」；在日本以香港身份立足，在香港成為日本通；在右派聚會強調和平，在左派則經常提及和安倍是好友。由此可見，她實在是一位人才，局長的不二之選。<br />\n<br />\n#周庭講兩句"},{"pid":"ee8de2b4301159b9621876d67ec742487e06f5b4","tid":222092,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dca80f0711bf8d5c782ceae93fdea2263c117dd","tid":222092,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"咁似伊索寓言隻蝙蝠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c9d568817388465b7e42d107032d672317e1e4","tid":222092,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade98fef0eacecb0bf4f72eed271f76ecadf2815","tid":222092,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉去到新加坡咁快撈唔掂要搵路返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2d2f22212feefc0edb1d177e8d79e8980aecea","tid":222092,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沈旭暉去到新加坡咁快撈唔掂要搵路返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一路有係fb打丁<img src=\"/ass